The Walton Group, Inc. (originally "The Walton Group, Inc. - Public Relations") is a corporation based in Provo, Utah. It is a full-service marketing firm that specializes in marketing and media relations for small businesses, nonprofit organizations, and government organizations (such as political campaigns). The Walton Group, Inc. is a historically significant business to Utah Valley. As the first public relations firm in Provo, The Walton Group, Inc. played a key role in the early economic development of Utah Valley, and is a key contributor to economic success today.
